Since mentioned characters are part of Unicode and are not known to ISO-8859-1 the expected behavior would be the same as when using XmlWriter so encoding the characters with their character entity references. I understand this would be a breaking change so probably this issue will get closed but perhaps someone will find this helpful in future.

